  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 138db3ffc7861704d8012aa6e86b9a09, type: 2}
  replyText:
  - Talk about myself? Fuck kinda question is that?
  - Ummmm, uhhhhhh...
  - Well, I love jokes! And puns. In fact, I got this *snick* funny in mind...
  - Umm, I guess my friends describe me as a forgetful person?
  - Myself? Like, what about myself should I talk about?
  - Oh, people like to make fun of me for tripping over my toes.
  - hmmm... i get called pessimistic, but i'm just facing reality unlike everyone
    else.
  - Oh well, my friends like to descrive me as the life of the party!
  - Oh, I really like tragic stories. They always bring tears to my eyes.
  - Oh, easy. I think I might have a sixth sense, with how in tune I am with everything
    around me.
  - Well, I guess I could say I'm a very romantic person. I've been searching for
    my soulmate for quite some time now.
  - Hmmm.. ohh! I love deodorant. Keeps me smelling good without having to take showers,
    which is hella annoying.
  - That's easy. I'm a very adaptable person. No matter the situation, I usually
    find a way out.
  - Oh, anything? So I could talk about fetishes? Not that I have any, of course.
  - Anything, huh... you can't comprehend the depths of my dark mind...
  - Hmm... I have really good pain tolerance. Like, really good.
  - Well, I want to give a good performance, so I really try to get into my role,
    become them.
  - Uh, people say I overreact a lot, but they're just simpleminded bores.
  - Wow, what a wonderful question! That'll help you learn about someone, for sure.
  - Oh, well, I love singing!
  - Myself? I guess I'm just a very...chill guy. I'm just nonchalant like that.
  - Myself, hm. I guess I could be very stern. Sometimes turns people off from me.
  - ANYTHING about myself? Let me just say, I would have went on and on, but I'll
    spare you the spiel. For now.
